      "text": [
        " اَلنَّبِيُّ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ : \"مَنِ اُبْتُلِيَ بِالْقَضَاءِ فَلْيُسَاوِ بَيْنَهُمْ فِي اَلْإِشَارَةِ وَ اَلنَّظَرِ فِي اَلْمَجْلِسِ \"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3242 - The Prophet (peace be upon him and his family) said:\n\"Whoever is tested with judging should treat them equally in gestures and glances within the gathering.\""
        ]
      }
